@ratchet1215 How about turn 1?  

Play the Depths, [Lotus Petal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotus Petal) or some other free way to add B to your mana pool, [Dark Ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Ritual), Hexmage, sacrifice.  

Congratulations. You now have a game ender on the first turn. Heck, if you use that leftover B on [Sol Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sol Ring) and tap that for a [Lightning Greaves](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Greaves) and attack for game.

